Developed a desktop-based To-Do List application using C++ with a graphical user interface that allows users to create, edit, delete, and organize tasks efficiently. 
Implemented features like due dates, and status tracking (completed/pending) to improve productivity and task management. 
Designed a clean and user-friendly interface to provide a smooth user experience, focusing on performance and data persistence. 


Green Background = Done.
Gray Background = Pending.
Click on 'X' to delete.
Click on 'O' to set as done or pending
